Keep Doin'
==========

Android app to easily do you tasks and to compare your success with friends.

Authors
-------

Michal Svec <kontakt@michalsvec.cz>
Jan Javorek <honza@javorek.net>
Pavel Zuna


Instalace a spusteni
--------------------


Pro spusteni aplikace je nutne mit spravne nainstalovane SDK a ADT plugin
pro Eclipse IDE.

Postup instalace: http://developer.android.com/sdk/installing.html

Dale je nutne pridat projekt do workspace:
File -> New -> Android Project

Create project from existing source - vybrat cestu do slozky KeepDoin/client/ 
a zadat nazev projektu. Napr. KeepDoin

Pak uz je mozne spustit aplikaci pomoci Run->Run

Pro beh aplikace je nutne Android API level 8. Je tedy nutne pripojit
telefon s Android 2.2 nebo vytvorit emulator s Google API 8.




